            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 1,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1489556875,
            "creation_date": 1489556875,
            "body": "<p>Yes, It is meant to handle several non-standard relationship mappings,  the <code>ElementCollection<\/code> can be used to define a one-to-many relationship and the <code>ElementCollection<\/code> values are always stored in a separate table. <\/p>\n",
